'''榆科'''共有8[[属|属]]约35[[种|种]]，主要分布在北半球[[温带|温带]]区域，大部分在[[亚洲|亚洲]]，没有原生于[[澳洲|澳洲]]的品种。[[中国|中国]]有8属50余种，分布于全国。<ref>{{cite web|last = Watson|first = L.|coauthors = Dallwitz, M. J.|title = The Families of Flowering Plants: Ulmaceae Mirb.|date = 1992 onwards|url = http://delta-intkey.com/angio/www/ulmaceae.htm|accessdate = 21 November 2006|archive-date = 2019-04-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190417122253/http://www.delta-intkey.com/angio/www/ulmaceae.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="stevens">{{cite web|last = Stevens|first = P|title = Angiosperm Phylogeny Website|publisher = Missouri Botanical Garden|date = 2001 onwards|url = http://www.mobot.org/mobot/research/APweb/welcome.html|accessdate = 21 November 2006|archive-date = 2010-02-06|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100206221914/http://www.mobot.org/mobot/research/apweb/welcome.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>1981年的[[克朗奎斯特分类法|克朗奎斯特分类法]]将其分在[[荨麻目|荨麻目]]中，1998年根据[[基因|基因]]亲缘关系分类的[[APG分类法|APG分类法]]认为应该分在[[蔷薇目|蔷薇目]]，并将[[朴属|朴属]]（''Celtis''）及相似的朴族几[[属|属]]另划入[[大麻科|大麻科]]（''Cannabaceae''）<ref name="stevens"/>

